data.name: lblDetailsProTurf
data.value: From sports fields and golf courses to highly managed landscapes, Aquatrols technologies help turfgrass professionals worldwide to conserve water and energy while producing high quality turfgrass. Our products ensure consistency in a variety of conditions and can serve as a strong basis for sustainable turf management practices.

data.name: lblDetailsAgriculture
data.value: Our unique water management chemistries allow agricultural producers to maximize irrigation efficiency and improve the efficacy of soil-applied chemicals. The result is improved crop productivity using less water and energy, effectively producing “more crop per drop.”

data.name: lblDetailsHorticulture
data.value: Soilless growing media producers and growers in the greenhouse and nursery industries rely on our unique products to create more desirable growing conditions. Aquatrols media wetting agents help growers improve plant quality, lower costs, and conserve water and other resources from production to point of sale.
